### **4. 33_LiveChartCanvas**  
**Description:**  
A real-time line chart generator for visualizing numeric data streams.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LiveChartCanvas - Real-Time Data Plotter

LiveChartCanvas creates animated graphs to monitor live metrics or simulated streams using Matplotlib.

## Features
- Live updating charts  
- Adjustable axis scaling  
- Works with API or sensor streams  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/33_LiveChartCanvas.git
cd 33_LiveChartCanvas
python visualize.py
